docs {
  This folder contains endpoints for managing project data, including
  
  - retrieving project details by ID,
      
  - listing projects by company,
      
  - adding project overviews with file uploads,
      
  - and updating project data with file attachments. Use these requests to perform CRUD operations and manage project-related resources efficiently.
}
